verbose_text: The same high dose of SB334867 also reduced the pressor (but not bradycardic) response to hypercapnia (20% CO2, a suffocation signal) as well as the tachycardic (but not pressor) response to the anxiogenic partial inverse benzodiazepine agonist FG7142.
